OL,5, A former government adviser on faith   
OL,6, has urged Rishi Sunak to apologise to  
OL,7, London Mayor Sadiq Khan after ex-Tory  
OL,8, deputy chairman Lee Anderson said he   
OL,9, was under the control of Islamists.    
OL,11,FColin Bloom told the BBC the comments  
OL,12,Fabout Mr Khan were "disgusting".       
OL,14,FMr Anderson was suspended from the     
OL,15,FConservative Party in Parliament after 
OL,16,Frefusing to apologise.                 
OL,18,FThe government said it was "clear there
OL,19,Fmust be zero tolerance for any form of 
OL,20,Fextremism, racism or hatred".          
